    "description": "The Cranite WirelessWall Client enables laptop, desktop, and handheld computer users to securely connect to WirelessWall-protected networks. The Client authenticates users, encrypts wireless network traffic, and blocks malicious attacks. Additionally, the Client optionally seamlessly roam from subnet to subnet without re-authenticating. The Client optionally integrates with the Windows logon, providing secure single signon functionality. Cranite's WirelessWall Client is simple to use and is validated to the government's rigorous FIPS-2 security standard.",
